📈 Stock Market App (Prototype)

A mobile app prototype that helps users track stock prices, manage portfolios, and stay updated with market news.  
Designed with Figma, this project demonstrates both UI/UX design skills and planning for future mobile development.

• Features
- 🔍 Real-time stock price tracking  
- 📊 Portfolio management  
- 📰 Latest market news feed  
- 🎨 Clean and user-friendly design  

